{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"So sometimes I get invited to give weird talks."},{"time":3000,"text":"I got invited to speak to the people"},{"time":6000,"text":"who dress up in big stuffed animal costumes"},{"time":9000,"text":"to perform at sporting events."},{"time":12000,"text":"Unfortunately I couldn't go."},{"time":14000,"text":"But it got me thinking about"},{"time":16000,"text":"the fact that these guys, at least most of them,"},{"time":19000,"text":"know what it is that they do for a living."},{"time":21000,"text":"What they do is they dress up"},{"time":23000,"text":"as stuffed animals and entertain people at sporting events."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27000,"text":"Shortly after that I got invited"},{"time":29000,"text":"to speak at the convention of the people"},{"time":31000,"text":"who make balloon animals."},{"time":33000,"text":"And again, I couldn't go. But it's a fascinating group. They make balloon animals."},{"time":36000,"text":"There is a big schism between the ones who make"},{"time":38000,"text":"gospel animals and porn animals, but --"},{"time":40000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":42000,"text":"they do a lot of really cool stuff with balloons."},{"time":45000,"text":"Sometimes they get in trouble, but not often."},{"time":47000,"text":"And the other thing about these guys"},{"time":49000,"text":"is, they also know what they do for a living."},{"time":52000,"text":"They make balloon animals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55000,"text":"But what do we do for a living?"},{"time":57000,"text":"What exactly to the people watching this do every day?"},{"time":62000,"text":"And I want to argue that what we do"},{"time":64000,"text":"is we try to change everything."},{"time":67000,"text":"That we try to find a piece of the status quo --"},{"time":70000,"text":"something that bothers us, something that needs to be improved,"},{"time":72000,"text":"something that is itching to be changed -- and we change it."},{"time":76000,"text":"We try to make big, permanent, important change."},{"time":81000,"text":"But we don't think about it that way."},{"time":83000,"text":"And we haven't spent a lot of time talking about"},{"time":85000,"text":"what that process is like."},{"time":88000,"text":"And I've been studying it for a couple years."},{"time":90000,"text":"And I want to share a couple stories with you today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92000,"text":"First, about a guy named Nathan Winograd."},{"time":94000,"text":"Nathan was the number two person at the San Francisco SPCA."},{"time":98000,"text":"And what you may not know about the history of the SPCA"},{"time":100000,"text":"is, it was founded to kill dogs and cats."},{"time":104000,"text":"Cities gave them a charter"},{"time":107000,"text":"to get rid of the stray animals on the street and destroy them."},{"time":110000,"text":"In a typical year four million dogs and cats were killed,"},{"time":114000,"text":"most of them within 24 hours of being scooped off of the street."},{"time":118000,"text":"Nathan and his boss saw this,"},{"time":120000,"text":"and they could not tolerate it."},{"time":122000,"text":"So they set out to make San Francisco"},{"time":124000,"text":"a no-kill city:"},{"time":126000,"text":"create an entire city"},{"time":128000,"text":"where every dog and cat,"},{"time":130000,"text":"unless it was ill or dangerous,"},{"time":133000,"text":"would be adopted, not killed."},{"time":135000,"text":"And everyone said it was impossible."},{"time":138000,"text":"Nathan and his boss went to the city council to get a change in the ordinance."},{"time":141000,"text":"And people from SPCAs and humane shelters around the country"},{"time":144000,"text":"flew to San Francisco"},{"time":146000,"text":"to testify against them --"},{"time":149000,"text":"to say it would hurt the movement and it was inhumane."},{"time":153000,"text":"They persisted. And Nathan went directly to the community."},{"time":157000,"text":"He connected with people who cared about this:"},{"time":159000,"text":"nonprofessionals, people with passion."},{"time":161000,"text":"And within just a couple years,"},{"time":163000,"text":"San Francisco became the first no-kill city,"},{"time":168000,"text":"running no deficit, completely supported by the community."},{"time":172000,"text":"Nathan left and went to Tompkins County, New York --"},{"time":175000,"text":"a place as different from San Francisco"},{"time":177000,"text":"as you can be and still be in the United States. And he did it again."},{"time":180000,"text":"He went from being a glorified dogcatcher"},{"time":182000,"text":"to completely transforming the community."},{"time":185000,"text":"And then he went to North Carolina and did it again."},{"time":187000,"text":"And he went to Reno and he did it again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":190000,"text":"And when I think about what Nathan did,"},{"time":192000,"text":"and when I think about what people here do, I think about ideas."},{"time":195000,"text":"And I think about the idea that"},{"time":198000,"text":"creating an idea, spreading an idea"},{"time":200000,"text":"has a lot behind it."},{"time":202000,"text":"I don't know if you've ever been to a Jewish wedding,"},{"time":205000,"text":"but what they do is, they take a light bulb"},{"time":208000,"text":"and they smash it."},{"time":211000,"text":"Now there is a bunch of reasons for that, and stories about it."},{"time":215000,"text":"But one reason is because it indicates a change,"},{"time":218000,"text":"from before to after."},{"time":220000,"text":"It is a moment in time."},{"time":222000,"text":"And I want to argue that we are living through"},{"time":225000,"text":"and are right at the key moment"},{"time":227000,"text":"of a change in the way ideas are created"},{"time":229000,"text":"and spread and implemented."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231000,"text":"We started with the factory idea:"},{"time":234000,"text":"that you could change the whole world if you had an efficient factory"},{"time":236000,"text":"that could churn out change."},{"time":238000,"text":"We then went to the TV idea,"},{"time":240000,"text":"that said if you had a big enough mouthpiece,"},{"time":242000,"text":"if you could get on TV enough times, if you could buy enough ads, you could win."},{"time":245000,"text":"And now we're in this new model of leadership,"},{"time":249000,"text":"where the way we make change"},{"time":252000,"text":"is not by using money"},{"time":255000,"text":"or power to lever a system,"},{"time":257000,"text":"but by leading."}]},{"cues":[{"time":259000,"text":"So let me tell you about the three cycles. The first one is the factory cycle."},{"time":262000,"text":"Henry Ford comes up with a really cool idea."},{"time":266000,"text":"It enables him to hire men"},{"time":268000,"text":"who used to get paid 50 cents a day"},{"time":270000,"text":"and pay them five dollars a day."},{"time":272000,"text":"Because he's got an efficient enough factory."},{"time":274000,"text":"Well with that sort of advantage"},{"time":276000,"text":"you can churn out a lot of cars."},{"time":278000,"text":"You can make a lot of change. You can get roads built."},{"time":281000,"text":"You can change the fabric of an entire country."},{"time":284000,"text":"That the essence of what you're doing is you need"},{"time":286000,"text":"ever-cheaper labor,"},{"time":288000,"text":"and ever-faster machines."},{"time":291000,"text":"And the problem we've run into is, we're running out of both."},{"time":294000,"text":"Ever-cheaper labor and ever-faster machines."},{"time":297000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":302000,"text":"So we shift gears for a minute,"},{"time":305000,"text":"and say, \"I know: television;"},{"time":308000,"text":"advertising. Push push."},{"time":310000,"text":"Take a good idea and push it on the world."},{"time":313000,"text":"I have a better mousetrap."},{"time":315000,"text":"And if I can just get enough money to tell enough people, I'll sell enough.\""},{"time":319000,"text":"And you can build an entire industry on that."},{"time":322000,"text":"If necessary you can put babies in your ads."},{"time":325000,"text":"If necessary you can use babies to sell other stuff."},{"time":328000,"text":"And if babies don't work, you can use doctors."},{"time":332000,"text":"But be careful."},{"time":334000,"text":"Because you don't want to get an unfortunate juxtaposition,"},{"time":336000,"text":"where you're talking about one thing instead of the other."},{"time":339000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":341000,"text":"This model requires you to act like the king,"},{"time":345000,"text":"like the person in the front of the room"},{"time":347000,"text":"throwing things to the peons in the back."},{"time":349000,"text":"That you are in charge, and you're going to tell people"},{"time":352000,"text":"what to do next."},{"time":354000,"text":"The quick little diagram of it is, you're up here,"},{"time":357000,"text":"and you are pushing it out to the world."},{"time":359000,"text":"This method -- mass marketing --"},{"time":362000,"text":"requires average ideas,"},{"time":364000,"text":"because you're going to the masses,"},{"time":366000,"text":"and plenty of ads."},{"time":369000,"text":"What we've done as spammers"},{"time":371000,"text":"is tried to hypnotize everyone"},{"time":373000,"text":"into buying our idea,"},{"time":375000,"text":"hypnotize everyone into donating to our cause,"},{"time":377000,"text":"hypnotize everyone into voting for our candidate."},{"time":380000,"text":"And, unfortunately, it doesn't work so well anymore either."},{"time":385000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":388000,"text":"But there is good news around the corner -- really good news."},{"time":393000,"text":"I call it the idea of tribes."},{"time":398000,"text":"What tribes are, is a very simple concept"},{"time":401000,"text":"that goes back 50,000 years."},{"time":404000,"text":"It's about leading and connecting people and ideas."},{"time":408000,"text":"And it's something that people have wanted forever."},{"time":411000,"text":"Lots of people are used to having a spiritual tribe, or a church tribe,"},{"time":415000,"text":"having a work tribe,"},{"time":417000,"text":"having a community tribe."},{"time":420000,"text":"But now, thanks to the internet, thanks to the explosion of mass media,"},{"time":423000,"text":"thanks to a lot of other things"},{"time":425000,"text":"that are bubbling through our society around the world,"},{"time":428000,"text":"tribes are everywhere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":430000,"text":"The Internet was supposed to homogenize everyone by connecting us all."},{"time":432000,"text":"Instead what it's allowed is silos of interest."},{"time":435000,"text":"So you've got the red-hat ladies over here."},{"time":437000,"text":"You've got the red-hat triathletes over there."},{"time":440000,"text":"You've got the organized armies over here."},{"time":442000,"text":"You've got the disorganized rebels over here."},{"time":444000,"text":"You've got people in white hats making food."},{"time":446000,"text":"And people in white hats sailing boats."},{"time":448000,"text":"The point is that you can find Ukrainian folk dancers"},{"time":451000,"text":"and connect with them,"},{"time":453000,"text":"because you want to be connected."},{"time":455000,"text":"That people on the fringes"},{"time":457000,"text":"can find each other, connect and go somewhere."},{"time":461000,"text":"Every town that has a volunteer fire department"},{"time":463000,"text":"understands this way of thinking."},{"time":465000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":471000,"text":"Now it turns out"},{"time":474000,"text":"this is a legitimate non-photoshopped photo."},{"time":477000,"text":"People I know who are firemen told me that this is not uncommon."},{"time":479000,"text":"And that what firemen do to train sometimes"},{"time":482000,"text":"is they take a house that is going to be torn down,"},{"time":484000,"text":"and they burn it down instead, and practice putting it out."},{"time":487000,"text":"But they always stop and take a picture."},{"time":489000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":490000,"text":"You know the pirate tribe is a fascinating one."},{"time":493000,"text":"They've got their own flag. They've got the eye patches."},{"time":495000,"text":"You can tell when you're running into someone in a tribe."},{"time":498000,"text":"And it turns out that it's tribes --"},{"time":500000,"text":"not money, not factories --"},{"time":502000,"text":"that can change our world, that can change politics,"},{"time":505000,"text":"that can align large numbers of people."},{"time":507000,"text":"Not because you force them to do something against their will,"},{"time":511000,"text":"but because they wanted to connect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":513000,"text":"That what we do for a living now,"},{"time":515000,"text":"all of us, I think,"},{"time":517000,"text":"is find something worth changing,"},{"time":519000,"text":"and then assemble tribes that assemble tribes"},{"time":524000,"text":"that spread the idea and spread the idea."},{"time":526000,"text":"And it becomes something far bigger than ourselves,"},{"time":528000,"text":"it becomes a movement."},{"time":531000,"text":"So when Al Gore set out"},{"time":533000,"text":"to change the world again,"},{"time":536000,"text":"he didn't do it by himself."},{"time":538000,"text":"And he didn't do it by buying a lot of ads."},{"time":540000,"text":"He did it by creating a movement."},{"time":543000,"text":"Thousands of people around the country"},{"time":545000,"text":"who could give his presentation for him,"},{"time":548000,"text":"because he can't be in 100 or 200 or 500 cities in each night."}]},{"cues":[{"time":553000,"text":"You don't need everyone."},{"time":556000,"text":"What Kevin Kelley has taught us is you just need,"},{"time":558000,"text":"I don't know, a thousand true fans --"},{"time":560000,"text":"a thousand people who care enough"},{"time":563000,"text":"that they will get you the next round"},{"time":566000,"text":"and the next round and the next round."},{"time":568000,"text":"And that means that the idea you create, the product you create,"},{"time":571000,"text":"the movement you create isn't for everyone,"},{"time":573000,"text":"it's not a mass thing. That's not what this is about."},{"time":575000,"text":"What it's about instead"},{"time":578000,"text":"is finding the true believers."},{"time":580000,"text":"It's easy to look at what I've said so far,"},{"time":583000,"text":"and say, \"Wait a minute, I don't have what it takes to be that kind of leader.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":586000,"text":"So here are two leaders. They don't have a lot in common."},{"time":591000,"text":"They're about the same age. But that's about it."},{"time":595000,"text":"What they did, though, is each in their own way,"},{"time":598000,"text":"created a different way"},{"time":602000,"text":"of navigating your way through technology."},{"time":604000,"text":"So some people will go out and get people to be on one team."},{"time":607000,"text":"And some people will get people to be on the other team."}]},{"cues":[{"time":610000,"text":"It also informs the decisions you make"},{"time":612000,"text":"when you make products or services."},{"time":614000,"text":"You know, this is one of my favorite devices."},{"time":617000,"text":"But what a shame that it's not organized"},{"time":619000,"text":"to help authors create movements."},{"time":622000,"text":"What would happen if, when you're using your Kindle,"},{"time":624000,"text":"you could see the comments and quotes and notes"},{"time":628000,"text":"from all the other people reading the same book as you in that moment."},{"time":631000,"text":"Or from your book group. Or from your friends, or from the circle you want."},{"time":634000,"text":"What would happen if authors, or people with ideas"},{"time":637000,"text":"could use version two, which comes out on Monday,"},{"time":640000,"text":"and use it to organize people"},{"time":643000,"text":"who want to talk about something."},{"time":645000,"text":"Now there is a million things I could share with you about the mechanics here."},{"time":648000,"text":"But let me just try a couple."}]},{"cues":[{"time":650000,"text":"The Beatles did not invent teenagers."},{"time":653000,"text":"They merely decided to lead them."},{"time":656000,"text":"That most movements, most leadership that we're doing"},{"time":659000,"text":"is about finding a group that's disconnected"},{"time":661000,"text":"but already has a yearning --"},{"time":663000,"text":"not persuading people to want something"},{"time":665000,"text":"they don't have yet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":667000,"text":"When Diane Hatz worked on \"The Meatrix,\""},{"time":671000,"text":"her video that spread all across the internet"},{"time":674000,"text":"about the way farm animals are treated,"},{"time":677000,"text":"she didn't invent the idea of being a vegan."},{"time":679000,"text":"She didn't invent the idea of caring about this issue."},{"time":681000,"text":"But she helped organize people,"},{"time":683000,"text":"and helped turn it into a movement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":685000,"text":"Hugo Chavez did not invent the disaffected"},{"time":688000,"text":"middle and lower class of Venezuela. He merely led them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":690000,"text":"Bob Marley did not invent Rastafarians."},{"time":693000,"text":"He just stepped up and said, \"Follow me.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":696000,"text":"Derek Sivers invented CD Baby,"},{"time":699000,"text":"which allowed independent musicians"},{"time":702000,"text":"to have a place to sell their music without selling out to the man --"},{"time":706000,"text":"to have place to take the mission"},{"time":708000,"text":"they already wanted to go to, and connect with each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":711000,"text":"What all these people have in common is that they are heretics."},{"time":715000,"text":"That heretics look at the status quo and say,"},{"time":717000,"text":"\"This will not stand. I can't abide this status quo."},{"time":720000,"text":"I am willing to stand up and be counted and move things forward."},{"time":724000,"text":"I see what the status quo is; I don't like it.\""},{"time":727000,"text":"That instead of looking at all the little rules"},{"time":729000,"text":"and following each one of them,"},{"time":732000,"text":"that instead of being what I call a sheepwalker --"},{"time":737000,"text":"somebody who's half asleep,"},{"time":739000,"text":"following instructions,"},{"time":741000,"text":"keeping their head down, fitting in --"},{"time":744000,"text":"every once in a while someone stands up and says, \"Not me.\""},{"time":747000,"text":"Someone stands up and says, \"This one is important."},{"time":751000,"text":"We need to organize around it.\""},{"time":754000,"text":"And not everyone will. But you don't need everyone."},{"time":757000,"text":"You just need a few people --"},{"time":759000,"text":"(Laughter) --"},{"time":763000,"text":"who will look at the rules,"},{"time":765000,"text":"realize they make no sense,"},{"time":768000,"text":"and realize how much they want to be connected."}]},{"cues":[{"time":770000,"text":"So Tony Hsieh does not run a shoe store."},{"time":773000,"text":"Zappos isn't a shoe store."},{"time":776000,"text":"Zappos is the one, the only,"},{"time":778000,"text":"the best-there-ever-was"},{"time":780000,"text":"place for people who are into shoes to find each other,"},{"time":784000,"text":"to talk about their passion,"},{"time":786000,"text":"to connect with people who care more"},{"time":788000,"text":"about customer service than making a nickel tomorrow."},{"time":791000,"text":"It can be something as prosaic as shoes,"},{"time":793000,"text":"and something as complicated as overthrowing a government."},{"time":795000,"text":"It's exactly the same behavior though."}]},{"cues":[{"time":799000,"text":"What it requires, as Geraldine Carter has discovered,"},{"time":802000,"text":"is to be able to say, \"I can't do this by myself."},{"time":805000,"text":"But if I can get other people to join my Climb and Ride,"},{"time":809000,"text":"then together we can get something that we all want."},{"time":814000,"text":"We're just waiting for someone to lead us.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":816000,"text":"Michelle Kaufman has pioneered"},{"time":818000,"text":"new ways of thinking about environmental architecture."},{"time":822000,"text":"She doesn't do it by quietly building one house at a time."},{"time":825000,"text":"She does it by telling a story"},{"time":828000,"text":"to people who want to hear it."},{"time":830000,"text":"By connecting a tribe of people"},{"time":832000,"text":"who are desperate to be connected to each other."},{"time":835000,"text":"By leading a movement and"},{"time":837000,"text":"making change."},{"time":839000,"text":"And around and around and around it goes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":841000,"text":"So three questions I'd offer you."},{"time":843000,"text":"The first one is, who exactly"},{"time":846000,"text":"are you upsetting?"},{"time":848000,"text":"Because if you're not upsetting anyone, you're not changing the status quo."},{"time":852000,"text":"The second question is, who are you connecting?"},{"time":855000,"text":"Because for a lot of people, that's what they're in it for:"},{"time":858000,"text":"the connections that are being made, one to the other."},{"time":862000,"text":"And the third one is, who are you leading?"},{"time":866000,"text":"Because focusing on that part of it --"},{"time":869000,"text":"not the mechanics of what you're building,"},{"time":871000,"text":"but the who, and the leading part -- is where change comes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":875000,"text":"So Blake, at Tom's Shoes, had a very simple idea."},{"time":879000,"text":"\"What would happen if every time someone bought a pair of these shoes"},{"time":884000,"text":"I gave exactly the same pair to someone"},{"time":886000,"text":"who doesn't even own a pair of shoes?\""},{"time":889000,"text":"This is not the story of how you get shelf space at Neiman Marcus."},{"time":893000,"text":"It's a story of a product that tells a story."},{"time":897000,"text":"And as you walk around with this remarkable pair of shoes"},{"time":899000,"text":"and someone says, \"What are those?\""},{"time":901000,"text":"You get to tell the story on Blake's behalf,"},{"time":903000,"text":"on behalf of the people who got the shoes."},{"time":905000,"text":"And suddenly it's not one pair of shoes or 100 pairs of shoes."},{"time":908000,"text":"It's tens of thousands of pairs of shoes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":910000,"text":"My friend Red Maxwell has spent the last 10 years"},{"time":913000,"text":"fighting against juvenile diabetes."},{"time":916000,"text":"Not fighting the organization that's fighting it -- fighting with them, leading them,"},{"time":919000,"text":"connecting them, challenging the status quo"},{"time":923000,"text":"because it's important to him."},{"time":925000,"text":"And the people he surrounds himself with need the connection."},{"time":930000,"text":"They need the leadership. It makes a difference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":933000,"text":"You don't need permission from people to lead them."},{"time":936000,"text":"But in case you do, here it is:"},{"time":939000,"text":"they're waiting, we're waiting"},{"time":942000,"text":"for you to show us where to go next."},{"time":945000,"text":"So here is what leaders have in common. The first thing is, they challenge"},{"time":948000,"text":"the status quo."},{"time":950000,"text":"They challenge what's currently there."},{"time":952000,"text":"The second thing is, they build a culture."},{"time":955000,"text":"A secret language, a seven-second handshake,"},{"time":958000,"text":"a way of knowing that you're in or out."},{"time":961000,"text":"They have curiosity. Curiosity about people in the tribe,"},{"time":964000,"text":"curiosity about outsiders. They're asking questions."},{"time":967000,"text":"They connect people to one another."},{"time":969000,"text":"Do you know what people want more than anything?"},{"time":971000,"text":"They want to be missed."},{"time":973000,"text":"They want to be missed the day they don't show up."},{"time":975000,"text":"They want to be missed when they're gone."},{"time":978000,"text":"And tribe leaders can do that."},{"time":980000,"text":"It's fascinating, because all tribe leaders have charisma,"},{"time":984000,"text":"but you don't need charisma to become a leader."},{"time":986000,"text":"Being a leader gives you charisma."},{"time":989000,"text":"If you look and study the leaders who have succeeded,"},{"time":992000,"text":"that's where charisma comes from -- from the leading."},{"time":994000,"text":"Finally, they commit."},{"time":997000,"text":"They commit to the cause. They commit to the tribe."},{"time":999000,"text":"They commit to the people who are there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1002000,"text":"So I'd like you to do something for me."},{"time":1005000,"text":"And I hope you'll think about it before you reject it out-of-hand."},{"time":1008000,"text":"What I want you to do, it only takes 24 hours,"},{"time":1012000,"text":"is: create a movement."},{"time":1014000,"text":"Something that matters. Start. Do it. We need it."},{"time":1018000,"text":"Thank you very much. I appreciate it."},{"time":1020000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}